ADDITIONAL NOTICES:

Smart Contract Security:
This project includes smart contracts that have NOT been professionally audited.
DO NOT deploy to mainnet or use with real funds without a comprehensive security
audit by qualified professionals. The authors assume no liability for any losses
incurred through the use of these contracts.

